Description: Tools for spatio-temporal modelling, visualization, and shrimp stock assessment,
    using customized delta-models and an ELU variant of the SPiCT framework. This package
    adapts/derives from SPiCT (GPL-3); see 'inst/COPYRIGHTS'.
